This paper focuses on the Winograd Schema Challenge, which is a test of machine intelligence and requires the use of commonsense knowledge and reasoning. This falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural networks (cs.NE).
